<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.10.8">
<l>maittakumā malarkkuḻalāy vaitēvī viṇṇappam</l>
<l>ottapukaḻ vāṉarakkō ṉuṭaṉiruntu niṉaittēṭa</l>
<l>attakucī rayōttiyarkō ṉaṭaiyāḷa mivaimoḻintāṉ</l>
<l>ittakaiyā laṭaiyāḷa mītavaṉkai mōtiramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lady with dark blossoms resembling kohl in [your] tresses!</l>
<l rend="indent">Vaidevī! Salutations.</l>
<l>When [he] thought to search [for you]</l>
<l rend="indent">along with the king of monkeys of equal fame</l>
<l>the king of Ayodhyā with befitting excellence</l>
<l rend="indent">spoke of these [incidents as] proof.</l>
<l>[But, the most] befitting proof is this, his ring!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
